saving highlights and performing trick plays on ncaa football how do you save highlights on ncaa football and how do you do trick plays such as the statue of liberty the hook and ladder and wide receiver passes for saving highlights how do you do it and how to you put them onto ea highlights i'm asking these questions for xbox i'm going to give you suggestions for the xbox since that's what i have and you didn't specify a platform to save highlights after a game is over you can select an option from the end of game menu to review every play from the game watch clips from different angles and save them as highlights this requires a memory device a hard drive memory card etc to do trick plays you select them from the playbook just like any other you can identify them as trick plays by the neon green lines that show up in the play an example of a frequently suggested one is the jet sweep go into the practice mode and take your time to explore the full playbook you'll find quite a few useful trick plays Mewtwo Pok__mon (anime) Legendary Pok__mon Pok__mon Crystal Pok__mon (video games) Pok__mon Abilities Missingno. Pok__mon: The Movie 2000 Pok__mon Trading Card Game Pok__mon Colosseum Celebi Pok__mon Gold and Silver Shiny Pok__mon Pok__mon FireRed and LeafGreen Lugia Charizard Pok__mon types Team Rocket Pok__mon XD: Gale of Darkness Vileplume Pok__mon 4Ever Viridian City Pok__mon Pok__mon Red and Blue Blastoise Pok__mon Ruby and Sapphire Venusaur Pok__mon Emerald Hitmonlee Dragonite Ho-Oh Dan Green Collectible card game Mew (Pok__mon) Giovanni (Pok__mon) Scyther Donphan Meganium Golduck Tauros Arcanine Latios Skarmory Fast bowling Suicune Parasect Orre Tyranitar Pok__mon Adventures Articuno Instant messaging Internet forum Trade union Boss (video games) Slowking Steelix Gyarados Pok__mon Yellow Charmander Jynx (Pok__mon) Pok__mon Chronicles Value at risk Nidoking ROM hacking Orange Islands Moltres Takeshi Kaga ZX Spectrum Medicham Mightyena Raichu Togepi Battle Frontier 